description:
Join us for a discussion on You Build It You Run It experiences, moderated by the co-author of the YBIYRI playbook Steve Smith.

[Read more about You Build It You Run It here.](https://www.equalexperts.com/our-services/deliver/you-build-it-you-run-it/)

**Moderator:**
Steve Smith
*Head of Scale service, Equal Experts*

**Panelists:**
Erin O'Connor
*Delivery Lead, Equal Experts*

Yasin Kothia
*Consultant, Equal Experts*

This talk will be recorded and the link to the recording added to the Comments shortly after the event.
title: You Build It You Run It.  What does it mean to engineers and delivery leads?
